    <h4>About</h4>
    <p style="text-indent: 20px;">This website pulls from a database containing information about a multitude of skills
        from videogames. The skills page lists all the skills in the database, and each skill name provides an attached link to a page 
        with more info about the skill, including a short video clip of the skill.
    </p>
