    <h4>Purpose</h4>
    <p style="text-indent: 20px;">
        I made this mainly because I love the creative ways videogames display techniques, skills, spells, technologies, etc., 
        and a site where you could search by name or game for different skills would be awesome. So far it only covers three 
        games and the sites functionality is limited, but I hope to make this into a well functioning website that allows the user 
        to easily search for videogame "skills" broadly speaking, and that it would elaborate and show the skill in action in its game.
    </p>
